title.en: Mofumofu Majuu to Heion ni Kurashitai no de Kowamote Koushaku no Kyuukon wa Okotowari desu
Akugyaku Seijo desu ga, Aisuru Danna-sama no Oyaku ni Tachitai desu. (To wa Ie, Kirawarete Iru no desu ga)
Ouhi ni Naru Yotei Deshita ga, Nise Seijo no Omei wo Kiserareta no de Toubou Shitara, Koutaishi ni Dekiai Saremashita. Sochira mo Douzo Oshiawase ni
Hikikomori Reijou wa Hanashi no Wakaru Seijuuban
Magaimo no Reijou Kara Aisare Kusushi ni Narimashita
Danna-sama ga Chicchai Mofumofu ni narimashita ~Watashi wo Akujo da to Gokai shiteita no ni, Subete Gibo no Uso da to Kizuita you desu~
Shukujo no Kagami Yamemashita. Toki wo Gyakkou shita Koushaku Reijou wa, Wagamama na Imouto ni Furimawasarenai you Seikaku Waruku Ikinobimasu!
Ee, Shoukansarete Komatteiru Seijo (Kari) to wa Watashi no Koto desu
Oshi ni Muchuu na Tensei Heroine desu ga, Mishiranu Momoiru Yurufuwa Ouji ni Dekiai Kouryakusareteimasu
Dare ni mo Aisarenai no de Yuka wo Migaite Itara Soko ga Seiiki-ka shita Reijou no Hanashi
Kokoro wo Tozashita Koushaku Kakka to Konyaku Shita Hazu na no ni, Naze ka Taisetsu ni Sasete Shimattemasu!
Zense Seijo datta Watashi wa Kusushi ni narimashita
